<section class="security-1">
  <article>
    <h1 class="hero-text">Security First.</h1>
    <h5 class="hero-text">ZokuVault helps families plan, organize, and share the important details of their lives.</h5>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="generic security-2">
  <article>
    <%= image_tag "marketing/lock.png", :class => "fr mt-20" %>
    <h1>Secure Access</h1>
    <p>We make sure it's you!  ZokuVault combines industry-leading complex password requirements, multi factor authentication, security question protocols and email verification to ensure that you and only you can access your account.</p>

    <h1>Encryption</h1>
    <p>Your data is encrypted using 256-bit Advanced Encryption Standard (AES-256), both on the way to your Vault and when stored in your Vault.</p>

    <h1>Control who sees what, and when</h1>
    <p>Only you control who has access to your information.  Any user to whom you grant access will follow our same strict secure access requirements.  We do not have access to your information, period.</p>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="generic-dark">
  <article>
    <h1>Secure Sharing</h1>
    <a class="superbutton short fr">
      <span class="text">Sign Up</span>
    </a>
    <p>Share your Vault strategically. Now that you have the basics or more entered, make sure to get this information into the hands of those that need to know.
      <ul>
        <li>Family</li>
        <li>Estate Planning Attorney</li>
        <li>Accountant</li>
        <li>Financial Advisor</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We are confident that you have done a great job creating a plan, and you can be confident in our ability to keep your data safe.</p>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="security-cta">
  <article>
    <h1 class="hero-text-dark">Your virtual safety deposit box and estate planning portal.</h1>
    <h5 class="hero-text-dark">We help store your digital assets safely and securely.</h5>
    <button class="primary-button call-to-action">Sign Up</button>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="security-3">


  <article>
    <%= image_tag "marketing/safe.png", :class => "fl" %>
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p>Your information is yours and yours alone.  We will not share it with or sell it to any third party without your expressed permission.  Please refer to our +Terms of Service+ and +Privacy Policy+.</p>
    <br>
    <h1>Monitoring</h1>
    <p>The ZokuVault team, and its partners, are actively receiving logs and monitoring for irregular activity, allowing for increased security and more effective incident response.</p>
  </article>
